									<h3>Archaeological excavations have revealed the oldest domestic dog remains ever reported in the Americas, roughly 11,000-year-old stone tools, and the tantalizing signs of far more to come.</h3>
									<p class="insidepagethumbinfodate">Dec 9, 2021 | 1,000 words, about 5 minutes</p>
								</header>
								</a>
